1
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:25,760
Su Xia, are you crazy?

2
00:01:35,789 --> 00:01:37,000
Ms. Jian.

3
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,240
You sure heard about it fast.

4
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,590
Did your dad tell you?

5
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:44,000
Nonsense.

6
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,710
I didn't even go back.

7
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:46,560
Shut up.

8
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,250
Aren't you leaving?

9
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:50,840
Go.

10
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,350
Bye-bye.

11
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:10,440
Alright, come down.

12
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,820
It's not that serious.

13
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:18,400
Who do you think did this?

14
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,630
The Jians.

15
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:24,120
I'll find a way back to Lu Fan.

16
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,370
Are you going to tell Lu Fan?

17
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,430
Now's not the time.

18
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:42,440
Look at the scar on her hand.

19
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,800
Do you know who took that knife

20
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,079
for you back then?

21
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,190
The bleeding has stopped.

22
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:47,120
It reopened an old injury.

23
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,630
She needs immediate surgery.

24
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:51,230
Otherwise, things could've
ended very badly.

25
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,079
Su Xia!

26
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,470
You've never understood me.

27
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:00,960
Right.

28
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,190
You, the high and mighty Mr. Lu,

29
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:04,650
always hand out your pity,

30
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,120
but you would never condescend

31
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,720
to try to understand anyone.

32
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,560
So you didn't know

33
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,560
I was never afraid.

34
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,150
Bro, what's going on so late at night?

35
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,079
Couldn't you say it over the phone?

36
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,870
I'm so sleepy.

37
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:24,590
I've been so busy.

38
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,710
Su Xia has an old injury on her wrist.

39
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,800
Did you know?

40
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,840
What injury? I don't know.

41
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,190
Hey, what's wrong?

42
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:44,410
Go help me find out what really happened.

43
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,870
The wound is healing well.

44
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:51,960
Thank you, doctor.

45
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,560
We'll be leaving now.

46
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,190
Okay, take care.

47
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:55,840
Okay.

48
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:02,190
Dad, there's something I haven't told you.

49
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,040
Actually, that day,

50
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:06,890
it was Su Xia who took the knife
for Lu Fan.

51
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,910
Su Xia?

52
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,630
She wasn't kidnapped.

53
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,680
Why was she there?

54
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,360
Exactly. I find it strange too.

55
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,079
That's why I didn't tell you.

56
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,290
The most important thing now is

57
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:28,300
not to let the Lu family find out
that it was Su Xia who did it.

58
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,070
But right now,

59
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:33,040
it seems the Lu family doesn't know it.

60
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,750
Su Xia didn't tell them.

61
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:35,950
No.

62
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:39,120
I think there's something off about her.

63
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:39,920
Right.

64
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,920
It was Su Xia who asked us out.

65
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,310
That day, after school,

66
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,280
we were kidnapped on the way.

67
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,800
Let's go. To the Lu family.

68
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:52,950
Speak up.

69
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:56,000
Who instructed you to help them

70
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,840
kidnap Young Master Lu?

71
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:00,870
Xia.

72
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,280
Is someone threatening you?

73
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,690
I will stand up for you.

74
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:08,360
Uncle Lu, I...

75
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,190
I...

76
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,390
Speak up.

77
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,880
Who exactly is targeting the Lu family?

78
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:17,310
Do you realize what you‘re doing?

79
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:18,630
It's kidnapping.

80
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,360
This is a crime!

81
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,190
If you don't talk,

82
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:24,120
we'll take you to the police station.

83
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,360
Xia, you...

84
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:26,870
Speak!

85
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,000
Speak!

86
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,330
I'll put her in isolation.

87
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,190
Let's go!

88
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,430
Dong, save me! Move!

89
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:41,120
And I want a full account

90
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:44,830
of Jian Xi's and everyone
in the Jian family's movements before,

91
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:48,560
during, and after the kidnapping.
Don't leave out a single detail.

92
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,560
Okay, I got it.

93
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,650
I'm leaving.

94
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,120
Hello, Dad.

95
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,960
Why did you call me so many times?

96
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,830
Did you handle it
from back then properly?

97
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:07,830
Lu Fan is already suspecting if I...

98
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,270
Xi, listen carefully.

99
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,720
Don't lose

100
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:13,720
the Lu family's support.

101
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,070
Some media are reporting

102
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,930
that our products have problems.

103
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,360
At a time like this, only the Lu family

104
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,390
can help us.

105
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:21,480
Whatever you do,

106
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,630
don't let Lu Fan slip away.

107
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:24,830
You're a woman.

108
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:27,390
You don't need me to teach you what to do.

109
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,000
Listen,

110
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:32,430
you two must get married
as soon as possible.

111
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,120
Ms. Jian.

112
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:54,000
The wedding dress you ordered has arrived.

113
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,460
Would you like to try it on?

114
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,480
Ms. Jian?

115
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:02,830
Coming in, Ms. Jian.

116
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:07,560
Ms. Jian?

117
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:11,040
Ms. Jian?

118
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:23,870
Ms. Jian!

119
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,480
Ms. Jian.

120
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,330
Ms. Jian, what's wrong?

121
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:30,800
Somebody help!

122
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,540
Why didn't you call an ambulance?

123
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,520
You're awake.

124
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,720
Lu Fan.

125
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,750
I didn't mean it.

126
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,150
I just didn't want to be useless.

127
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,150
Lu Fan, I know.

128
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:43,720
They...

129
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,790
They all say you don't want to marry me

130
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:47,510
just because I'm a cripple.

131
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,980
I know the Jian family
is not good enough for you.

132
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:55,270
I'm a cripple, and I'm not good enough
for you, either.

133
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:57,120
I won't be a burden to you.

134
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,200
I'll disappear.

135
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,550
I'll disappear.

136
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,720
If I disappear, everything will be fine.

137
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,360
I just...

138
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:06,000
I just want to...

139
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:12,750
Don't worry.

140
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,480
I will marry you.

141
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:20,640
No one will attack you with this again.

142
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,630
Come on.

143
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,550
If you're afraid of

144
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:40,030
people seeing this scar,

145
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,700
I'll arrange a scar removal surgery
for you.

146
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:53,960
Mr. Lu.

147
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,870
Did Ms. Jian's right hand

148
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,240
suffer severe trauma?

149
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,040
What's wrong?

150
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:59,510
She cut her wrist multiple times.

151
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,360
I can tell

152
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:02,320
she hasn't come to terms
with the scar on her hand.

153
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,360
There's a good chance

154
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:05,760
her psychological issues are linked to it.

155
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,030
Hello, Fan.

156
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,080
Hello.

157
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:28,000
Is the psychiatrist you mentioned

158
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,360
still available?

159
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:31,510
I've already contacted

160
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:33,960
the internationally renowned expert,
Dr. G.

161
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:36,320
But she's a bit hard to deal with,

162
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,790
and she ignored me.

163
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,440
But don't worry.

164
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:41,040
I'll figure something out.

165
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:43,600
Get her appointment as soon as possible.

166
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,200
I want to find out whether she

167
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,570
actually has a mental illness.

168
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,270
You are so busy.

169
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:09,440
You don't have to make time just for me.

170
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,240
It's okay. I've got time.

171
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:19,870
Hello, Xiao Qi.

172
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:21,800
Come find me at the clinic quickly.

173
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:24,030
Hello, are you Dr. G?

174
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,280
Wait a minute.

175
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:48,720
The patient's family, please wait outside.

176
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:51,120
Famous doctors might all have some quirks.

177
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:53,040
Why don't you wait outside?

178
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,670
Please cooperate.

179
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,460
Otherwise, I'll decline the consultation.

180
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:11,750
Dr. G.

181
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:16,320
Doctor, please take a close look.

182
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:19,630
Look carefully.

183
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,720
You're out.

184
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:40,030
Jian Xi doesn't look sick at all.

185
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,240
But

186
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:43,760
I've been running around like crazy
trying

187
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,770
to get you an appointment with her.

188
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,440
Fill out the test form on the table.

189
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,000
Is everything set?

190
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,240
I want the truth.

191
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:13,440
Fan, you have to believe in Dr. G.

192
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,150
She'll know right away

193
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,550
whether it's real or not.

194
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:21,240
Then, how much do you know about Dr. G?

195
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:24,120
It seems Mr. Lu is also
interested in Dr. G.

196
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:29,650
Looks like your fiancée
isn't enough for you.

197
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,080
You already have a new target so quickly.

198
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,790
You know what they say:

199
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:35,510
"curiosity killed the cat"?

200
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,150
Mr. Xiao.

201
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:41,590
Are you also here to see a doctor?

202
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:45,030
I am actually very curious
about the doctor

203
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,870
who can treat you.

204
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:51,840
Ms. Jian, you've done?

205
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,600
Are you Jianxi's family?

206
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,510
Here is the diagnosis.

207
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:21,100
Dr. G prescribed some antidepressants.

208
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,780
Follow me to get the medicine.

209
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,330
Don't worry, Mr. Lu.

210
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,150
With Xia keeping me company,

211
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:32,510
I'm having a great time.

212
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,870
Fan, let's go.

213
00:14:54,030 --> 00:14:55,630
Why didn't you tell Lu Fan

214
00:14:56,150 --> 00:14:58,150
that Jian Xi was faking her illness?

215
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,690
Since she loves acting so much,

216
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:02,910
let's play along to the very end.

217
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,910
Great.

218
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,490
I'll give you a little push.

219
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:17,320
Dad.

220
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,680
He took me to see the doctor again today.

221
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,270
What should I do?

222
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,240
Haven't you talked to him
about getting married yet?

223
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:29,150
I have. I've asked him to come with me
to try on wedding dresses several times,

224
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:31,350
but he always comes up with some excuse.

225
00:15:33,790 --> 00:15:34,670
Do you think he found out about

226
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:36,240
what happened back then?

227
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:39,150
I don't think I left

228
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:41,320
any evidence behind.

229
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:44,240
But all it takes is one mistake.

230
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,120
We can't wait any longer.

231
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:51,960
We can't put this off any longer.

232
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,000
married immediately.
